# @title 用户登录完整流程
# @desc 从用户输入账号密码到完成登录的完整流程，含验证码、token 刷新
# @icon 🔐
# @meta 节点数:7个|分支:2个|关键:token存储
graph TD
    Start([开始]) --> Input[输入账号密码]
    Input --> Validate{验证格式?}
    Validate -->|失败| ShowError[显示错误提示]
    ShowError --> Input
    Validate -->|成功| CheckCode{验证码?}
    CheckCode -->|需要| VerifyCode[校验验证码]
    VerifyCode -->|失败| ShowCodeError[验证码错误]
    ShowCodeError --> Input
    VerifyCode -->|成功| Auth[调用认证服务]
    CheckCode -->|不需要| Auth
    Auth -->|失败| ShowAuthError[认证失败]
    ShowAuthError --> Input
    Auth -->|成功| GenerateToken[生成Token]
    GenerateToken --> SaveToken[存储Token]
    SaveToken --> Success([登录成功])

    classDef start fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:2px
    classDef process fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#6b7280,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:2px
    classDef end fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#22c55e,stroke-width:2px
    classDef error fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444,stroke-width:2px

    class Start,End end
    class Input,Validate,CheckCode,Auth,GenerateToken,SaveToken process
    class ShowError,ShowCodeError,ShowAuthError error
    class Decision,VerifyCode decision
